import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { motion } from 'framer-motion'; import { Settings, Play, Square, RotateCcw, BarChart3, History, Users, Clock, TrendingUp, AlertTriangle, CheckCircle, Activity, Zap, Brain, RefreshCw } from 'lucide-react'; import { LineChart, Line, XAxis, YAxis, CartesianGrid, Tooltip, ResponsiveContainer, BarChart, Bar } from 'recharts'; const PerformancePage = ({ onNavigate }) => { const [testConfig, setTestConfig] = useState({ type: 'Load Test', url: 'http://localhost:3000', users: 100, duration: 60, rampUp: 10, thinkTime: 1000 }); const [isTestRunning, setIsTestRunning] = useState(false); const [testProgress, setTestProgress] = useState(0); const [realTimeData, setRealTimeData] = useState({ activeUsers: 100, avgResponseTime: 443, successRate: 90, requestsPerSec: 15 }); const [testResults, setTestResults] = useState({ totalRequests: 200, successfulRequests: 190, failedRequests: 10, avgResponseTime: 309, percentile95: 542, peakRPS: 56 }); const [responseTimeData] = useState([ { range: '0-100ms', count: 20 }, { range: '100-200ms', count: 34 }, { range: '200-300ms', count: 24 }, { range: '300-400ms', count: 15 }, { range: '400-500ms', count: 2 }, { range: '500ms+', count: 1 } ]); const [requestsOverTime] = useState([ { time: '41s', requests: 35 }, { time: '43s', requests: 10 }, { time: '45s', requests: 55 }, { time: '47s', requests: 10 }, { time: '49s', requests: 25 }, { time: '51s', requests: 40 }, { time: '53s', requests: 55 }, { time: '55s', requests: 30 }, { time: '57s', requests: 20 }, { time: '59s', requests: 25 } ]); const [monitoringData] = useState([ { time: 0, responseTime: 550, requests: 45 }, { time: 5, responseTime: 300, requests: 60 }, { time: 10, responseTime: 450, requests: 35 }, { time: 15, responseTime: 350, requests: 50 }, { time: 20, responseTime: 500, requests: 25 }, { time: 25, responseTime: 400, requests: 40 }, { time: 30, responseTime: 550, requests: 30 }, { time: 35, responseTime: 380, requests: 45 }, { time: 40, responseTime: 320, requests: 55 }, { time: 45, responseTime: 480, requests: 35 } ]); const [testHistory, setTestHistory] = useState([ { type: "Load Test", users: 100, status: "completed", successRate: 98, message: "Completed successfully with 98% success rate", timestamp: "Just now" }, { type: "Stress Test", users: 500, status: "warning", successRate: 85, message: "High CPU usage detected, 85% success rate", timestamp: "2 hours ago" } ]); useEffect(() => { let interval; if (isTestRunning) { interval = setInterval(() => { setTestProgress(prev => { if (prev >= 100) { setIsTestRunning(false); return 100; } return prev + 1; }); }, 100); } return () => clearInterval(interval); }, [isTestRunning]); const handleStartTest = () => { setIsTestRunning(true); setTestProgress(0); }; const handleStopTest = () => { setIsTestRunning(false); }; const handleReset = () => { setTestConfig({ type: 'Load Test', url: 'http://localhost:3000', users: 100, duration: 60, rampUp: 10, thinkTime: 1000 }); setIsTestRunning(false); setTestProgress(0); }; return (
{/* Header */}

setTestConfig(prev => ({ ...prev, url: e.target.value }))} className="w-full bg-gray-800 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent" />
setTestConfig(prev => ({ ...prev, users: parseInt(e.target.value) || 0 }))} className="w-full bg-gray-800 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent" />
setTestConfig(prev => ({ ...prev, duration: parseInt(e.target.value) || 0 }))} className="w-full bg-gray-800 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent" />
setTestConfig(prev => ({ ...prev, rampUp: parseInt(e.target.value) || 0 }))} className="w-full bg-gray-800 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent" />
setTestConfig(prev => ({ ...prev, thinkTime: parseInt(e.target.value) || 0 }))} className="w-full bg-gray-800 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent" />

Start Test Stop Test Reset
